Type	TV Series, 24 episodes
Year	07.10.2005 till 31.03.2006
Categories	Action, Androids, Bounty Hunters, Mecha, Post-apocalyptic, Power Suits, SciFi, Tragedy, Underworld, Violence 

Scenario by Noboru Kimura (My Hime, Dandoh!) 
Character design and art direction by Shuzilow.HA (Twinbee series) 
Concept design by Kenichi Sonoda (Bubblegum Crisis, Gunsmith Cats) 
Planning by Shuzilow.HA and Gonzo 
Production by Gonzo 

Solty is a robot girl who is living with Roy, a bounty hunter. By the encounter of various people, she begins to behave like a human. However, at the same time, she realizes that she is not a human. 
When the secret of Solty is revealed, she and the other people will be involved in the plot...
